WTP runtime I20050422

1. open 3 source editors
2. type something in last editor opened
3. type something in the first editor opened
4. hit ctrl+shift+f4 to close all editors
5. you get a save resources dialog asking if you want to save the editors that 
are still dirty
6. pause for about 3 secs..
7. hit deselect all
8. hit ok

you end up with the exception below.  this seems like a tricky timing bug.
